60
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,020
than your ex-husband.

61
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,700
Ms. Sheng is right.

62
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:17,000
So I started thinking

63
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,660
