I'm out here sipping tea,
doing flower arrangements,

66
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,940
and hitting all the tourist spots.

67
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,860
But is that me?

68
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,640
