but Dad said no.

107
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:41,600
Those stories

108
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,420
were everywhere back then.

109
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:45,120
Eventually,

110
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,659
everyone just assumed

111
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,340
your dad cheated

112
